  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK961">
<l>iṉṟi yamaiyāc ciṟappiṉ vāyiṉuṅ</l>
<l> kuṉṟa varupa viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Actions that would degrade (one's) family should not be done; though they may be so important that not doing them would end in death.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
